Document: OpenXRActionBindingModifier
Path: godot/classes/class_openxractionbindingmodifier.rst
Summary: A binding modifier that applies on individual actions related to an interaction profile.

Inherits: OpenXRBindingModifier < Resource < RefCounted < Object
Inherited By: OpenXRAnalogThresholdModifier

Binding modifier that applies on individual actions related to an interaction profile. This class modifies how specific actions are bound within an interaction profile, allowing customization of input behavior for individual action mappings. It inherits from OpenXRBindingModifier and is extended by OpenXRAnalogThresholdModifier for specialized analog input handling.
